He is talking about birth certificate of the receiver, that he has problems getting. He talks about some government officer Dawood Sahib who is helping him and talking about some magistrate who will help get the certificate. The receiver is some student because at the end of the letter, he talks about being calm during exams etc. The writer is not a native speaker of Urdu. He makes many spelling mistakes. Also his urdu is not good. It has a Bengali, Meemon kind of accent.
